name: techytree technologies
overview: Techy Tree is a technology consulting and training company delivering the professional services of experienced Professionals and academicians to clients and students across the globe. The inception of Techy Tree Technologies is in lieu of the ever growing demand for skilled manpower in high end technologies like TIBCO(EAI,BPM,SOA),IBM( IBM Business Process Manager Advanced V7.5,Websphere Lombardi BPM 7.5),ORACLE( Oracle Fusion,SOA,OSB,AIA,BPM),SoftwareAG(webmethods),Pega(Business Process Management) and radical growth in data is what all the technocrats dread to handle. The training and solutions provided by Techytree allows its students and clients to meet these challenges with ease. We give much more in value than what we take in payment. The training given by us far exceeds the expectation of our students and so are our services to our clients.
